Author: Andys
Content:
I completely agree. Some people don't seem to care about standing up and can talk for hours.

I personally think the best meetings are where I can keep working at my PC while I listen in on the meeting conversation. This way I reach the end of the meeting having kept abreast of other developments and also fixed some bugs at the same time.
